quantity.name: ball_berry_slope
quantity.units: dimensionless from [mol / m^2 / s] / [mol / m^2 / s]

quantity.name: DVI
quantity.units: dimensionless; development index, see Osborne et al. 2015

quantity.name: heightf
quantity.units: m^-1 from (m^2 / m^2) / m. Leaf area density; LAI per height of canopy.

quantity.name: lai
quantity.units: dimensionless from (m^2 leaf) / (m^2 ground). LAI of entire canopy.

quantity.name: maturity_group
quantity.units: dimensionless; maturity group of soybean cultivar

quantity.name: nir_incident_direct
quantity.units: J / (m^2 beam) / s [area perpendicular to beam]

quantity.name: par_incident_direct
quantity.units: J / (m^2 beam) / s [area perpendicular to beam]

quantity.name: rateSeneLeaf
quantity.units: dimensionless, maximum percentage of leaf senesced at a given timestep

quantity.name: rateSeneRhizome
quantity.units: dimensionless, maximum percentage of rhizome senesced at a given timestep

quantity.name: rateSeneRoot
quantity.units: dimensionless, maximum percentage of root senesced at a given timestep

quantity.name: rateSeneStem
quantity.units: dimensionless, maximum percentage of stem senesced at a given timestep

quantity.name: solar
quantity.units: micromol / (m^2 beam) / s [area perpendicular to beam]

quantity.name: solar_energy_absorbed_leaf
quantity.units: W / m^2 [should include losses to soil / lower canopy layers]

quantity.name: Tbase_emr
quantity.units: degrees C; base temp for thermal time from sowing to emergence

quantity.name: time
quantity.units: time expressed as a fractional day of year

quantity.name: TTemr
quantity.units: degrees C * days, thermal time from sowing to emergence

quantity.name: TTemr_threshold
quantity.units: degrees C * days; accumulated thermal time for emergence

quantity.name: TTrep
quantity.units: degrees C * days, thermal time of reproductive states

quantity.name: TTveg
quantity.units: degrees C * days, thermal time of vegetative states
